3/3(日)  蒲崗村道公園</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n0930 <span style=\"color: purple;\">伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學</span> 對 <span style=\"color: green;\">南島中學</span>  [/red]<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">(oncc睇體 「傑志學界足球台」直播)</span></strong><br />\n1100 <span style=\"color: red;\">港島中學</span> 對 <span style=\"color: purple;\">賽馬會體藝中學</span> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">收看直播方法：</span></strong><br />\noncc睇體 <br />\n<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/?section=20180006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2F%3Fsection%3D20180006&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=9acc2789\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/?section=20180006</a><br />\n睇體 Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%9D%87%E9%AB%94-ontv-Sports-314737122692285/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%25AB%2594-ontv-Sports-314737122692285%2F&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=c5518bce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%9D%87%E9%AB%94-ontv-Sports-314737122692285/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">評述：劉舜文、董之英學生</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><strong><ins>季軍賽：6/3(三) 0930 蒲崗村道公園</ins></strong></ins></span>  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>決賽： 9/3(六)  旺角大球場</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.pyicorp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/PYE-img02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pyicorp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FPYE-img02.jpg&h=5de94f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1400 <strong>學界精英足球賽 決賽</strong> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: maroon;\">(港台電視32直播)</span></ins></strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">(ONCC睇體直播)</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">(UPOWER/YAHOO直播)</span><br />\n1600 <strong>大專盃決賽</strong> 香港理工大學 VS 香港教育大學 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: maroon;\">(港台電視32直播)</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jcex7cY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcex7cY.jpg&h=24b14b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fPm1f7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPm1f7A.jpg&h=04aca553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2493877/org/0ae17707bdbcc5aae12956e1acfae862.jpg/iMrMB8C4qdWOw0vDATFK064IjQKK7UEpm883KZvPNyk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2493877%2Forg%2F0ae17707bdbcc5aae12956e1acfae862.jpg%2FiMrMB8C4qdWOw0vDATFK064IjQKK7UEpm883KZvPNyk&h=9fdf3887&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"39115203c09c9b57693a0ff808129e58e70a65e0","tid":1042280,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>次圈(八強)詳細戰報</ins></span></strong><br />\n0900 1號場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學</strong></span> 0：1 <span style=\"color: red;\">喇沙書院</span> </span>1號場<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dEYaMN_WRhb9G0EMWOTMBQ-~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/cfa345586977cd75def8e51896984d6e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdEYaMN_WRhb9G0EMWOTMBQ-~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fcfa345586977cd75def8e51896984d6e&h=e434ff32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全場片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/314737122692285/videos/308423039871898/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F314737122692285%2Fvideos%2F308423039871898%2F&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=8d66b4c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/314737122692285/videos/308423039871898/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OSP190228-11849-101-M&amp;d=1551327324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DOSP190228-11849-101-M%26d%3D1551327324&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=64beec4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OSP190228-11849-101-M&amp;d=1551327324</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OPS190228-11849-102-M&amp;d=1551328457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DOPS190228-11849-102-M%26d%3D1551328457&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=f9ef898a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OPS190228-11849-102-M&amp;d=1551328457</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">今仗有三位董之英學生為觀眾聲音導航，其中已有評述經驗的潘澤霆今次有新體會：「首先要忘記自己是董之英學生，雖然湯國華上輪淘汰我們，但做評述一上場就要保持客觀，抽起個人情感去分析比賽。」至於初次評述的蔡子健在短短兩小時直播看到自己的進步：「第一次做評述，開始時較緊張，不敢出聲。但後來嘗試放膽講，講順了便無再怯場，整體來説我滿意自己表現。」</span></em><br />\n<br />\n上輪多支強隊遭淘汰後，爭冠形勢變得更混亂。這天再出現爆冷戰果，伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學成功延續神奇之旅，繼上輪擊敗董之英中學，今場再以一球小勝喇沙書院，歷史性殺入精英賽四強。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2493364/org/be2734e3168582a19043eb5edacf7268.jpg/-cokn-IpUikkbeMY3A_7_O4wlyocPqebf-MgQVXjIEE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2493364%2Forg%2Fbe2734e3168582a19043eb5edacf7268.jpg%2F-cokn-IpUikkbeMY3A_7_O4wlyocPqebf-MgQVXjIEE&h=f5e71bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗區亞軍湯國華上兩輪同樣戰至互射十二碼階段，淘汰匯知中學及去屆季軍董之英，八強面對港九區D1球隊喇沙，湯國華沿用上輪淘汰董之英的陣容出戰。喇沙上半場可謂佔盡優勢，僅4分鐘便出現首腳中目標射門，不過洪朗彥的遠射被門將吳字安沒收。表現活躍的喇沙翼鋒蘇荻安成為球隊上半場的進攻泉源，13分鐘有一腳直射罰球惟同樣被門將接實。3分鐘後，張展誠遠柱接應角球轉身抽射同樣無功而還。喇沙在25分鐘獲得最黃金機會，不過蘇荻安接應傳中的頭搥攻門中柱不入，最終在湯國華未有射門下兩隊互交白卷完半場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HxL4CZDdzYiPnR.Xif.Lcw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/d2a149c4d37b5240a2391b3bf372b875\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHxL4CZDdzYiPnR.Xif.Lcw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fd2a149c4d37b5240a2391b3bf372b875&h=890f2954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2493361/org/7257fb6ed59158c71a7216a696b47dfd.jpg/I556AXiK5oTHlRNCEiG2GfWzK4iEwFfbkLVKFbq1ShU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2493361%2Forg%2F7257fb6ed59158c71a7216a696b47dfd.jpg%2FI556AXiK5oTHlRNCEiG2GfWzK4iEwFfbkLVKFbq1ShU&h=9534fff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然湯國華上半場難越喇沙後場，不過換邊後4分鐘卻意外地打開紀錄，陳浩然的後場罰球吊入禁區，喇沙門將林宗瀚在隊友稍為干擾下甩手，後備入替的黃啓聰射入空門。落後的喇沙隨即反攻，蘇荻安8分鐘後再在禁區內起腳惟亦未能追和。喇沙在餘下時間繼續控制中場，不過前線的把握力卻成致命傷。李卓衡17分鐘禁區內無人看管下頂高，加上劉君正12分鐘後同樣在小禁區頂射高，宣布喇沙最終1球不敵湯國華，後者首度打入四強。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2493468/org/d2c3ca0ff7f1040cf62863eec135eca7.jpg/rGTjkBJaH-yjTIdpeykBG7E-G8ANgItlIvp4vCL6eLw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2493468%2Forg%2Fd2c3ca0ff7f1040cf62863eec135eca7.jpg%2FrGTjkBJaH-yjTIdpeykBG7E-G8ANgItlIvp4vCL6eLw&h=f517cfb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2019/02/20190228_JingYing_TKWSS_9_up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2019%2F02%2F20190228_JingYing_TKWSS_9_up.jpg&h=b8984ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n球員賽後難掩興奮心情，門將吳子安更喜極而泣。門將吳子安更流下淚水，他形容自己心情激動：「人生首次入精英賽4強，感覺相當難忘，很難形容這刻的心情。球隊全程受壓，對方有不少是港隊成員，攻力強勁，但我們全力做好防守，終能取勝。」<br />\n<br />\n而入球功臣黃啟聰雖然第二次參與精英賽，但今屆才是第一年上場，今仗後備入替，教練給他一個簡單而重要的任務：「教練著我落場不要躲懶，要多跑動。即使實力上有差距，都要保持上場對董之英的心態，搏盡，不輕易放棄。」他的努力最後亦得到回報，射入今年學界的第一球。「那時沒有想太多，很怕撻Q，因為面對空龍一定要射入。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2493462/org/8b60ac0d208f7a5a8e28885a32e63783.jpg/DnCrdgV0sJIs5_4j5qpmcBsvKgV-Cpug9BQet_QUHrc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2493462%2Forg%2F8b60ac0d208f7a5a8e28885a32e63783.jpg%2FDnCrdgV0sJIs5_4j5qpmcBsvKgV-Cpug9BQet_QUHrc&h=794cd7a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5db3b64d10526ad6b3da7e4c9d070ca93ef44928","tid":1042280,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:42:58.000Z","msg":"0900 2號場 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">觀塘瑪利諾書院</span> 0：3 <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>南島中學</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2019/02/20190228_JingYing_KTMC_1_up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2019%2F02%2F20190228_JingYing_KTMC_1_up.jpg&h=e56593fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下半塲精華<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ik0eUXInDu4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIk0eUXInDu4&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=eed868cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ik0eUXInDu4</a><br />\n於D1取得第5名的南島中學八強遇上觀塘瑪利諾書院，上半場憑Paul Sauli 23分鐘的入球領先。換邊後Paul Sauli再入1球，加上Liam完場前7分鐘「埋齋」，南島3球大勝晉級。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tCqmj2LXW7YKHus.lfJsig--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/40365bcce67276c71b9c81e16281a9a7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtCqmj2LXW7YKHus.lfJsig--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F40365bcce67276c71b9c81e16281a9a7&h=bfe791f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然觀瑪8強止步，但已創出他們精英賽最好成績，首年接手球隊A Grade的鄧Sir滿意球隊這日發揮：「這日我們以防守反擊為主，球員在全場受壓下做好每一次的防守，雖然未能晉級但滿意他們表現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2019/02/20190228_JingYIng_KTMC_4_up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2019%2F02%2F20190228_JingYIng_KTMC_4_up.jpg&h=8ece6fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40c045df3f4e07deff4bb25f548baecee30a00f3","tid":1042280,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"1030 1號場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港青基信書院 1：3 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港島中學</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FGecbBfXDYADP2DUpi50og--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/a8a613f45d98a4da01da33e8fdcb6f84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFGecbBfXDYADP2DUpi50og--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fa8a613f45d98a4da01da33e8fdcb6f84&h=15898f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全場精華<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m89OgNe4nwk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm89OgNe4nwk&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=96bde42f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m89OgNe4nwk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BvtfOffkiup9q8gcQ_5bWA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/bdfb918964e6af340e3abee97b6119bc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBvtfOffkiup9q8gcQ_5bWA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fbdfb918964e6af340e3abee97b6119bc&h=60bd43f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港島中學上演反勝劇本<br />\n<br />\n他們上半場15分鐘被港青基信書院的Zachary Ford 離門廿多離射入「世界波」，半場以1球落後。不過港島中學在換邊後13分鐘就由Gwenael Laot追和，其後再有Samuel Pijpers「梅開二度」，當中個人第2球入球更是「1扭4」的金球，最終以3：1反勝去屆殿軍基信，首度闖入四強。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/52335234_2121153994773701_8084049137441439744_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=9cd4eaa03d5170e679da781f49629b1f&amp;oe=5D23ADFF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F52335234_2121153994773701_8084049137441439744_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D9cd4eaa03d5170e679da781f49629b1f%26oe%3D5D23ADFF&h=d7eb3e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wnbvTu.K9XMElvc0ID9GeA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/346e077918bef9514817b2aa2b12d517\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwnbvTu.K9XMElvc0ID9GeA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F346e077918bef9514817b2aa2b12d517&h=f3a5dd38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cb514c0b9fb91c6b6a21396959eb1bf400a5e0a","tid":1042280,"uid":99872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"錯呀<br />\n次圈(八強)詳細戰報<br />\n0900 1號場<br />\n伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學 0：1 喇沙書院 1號場<br />\n<br />\n係1:0至真"},{"pid":"ab52db9ac67d41c4a8bf703a29ff98a1ec2c2607","tid":1042280,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7cb514c0b9fb91c6b6a21396959eb1bf400a5e0a","tid":1042280,"uid":99872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"錯呀<br />\n次圈(八強)詳細戰報<br />\n0900 1號場<br />\n伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學 0：1 喇沙書院 1號場<br />\n<br />\n係1:0至真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"睇左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f721ed5cb075838b55cc00eb00c66599947ee19","tid":1042280,"uid":86,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"仲諗住<br />\n四強會有三隊鬼仔<br />\n點知咁好睇"},{"pid":"8510f2e6ac7c5292d37fbf0f350de4160f629dd2","tid":1042280,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"1030 2號場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 哈羅香港國際學校 0：4 <span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>賽馬會體藝中學</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2494187/org/fe41eb13a9cec86545c6f901456305f8.jpg/PRa3H7aNGM3mYWrS2a6B5gU3PoqeuqSFSPOT_2Lzk_8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2494187%2Forg%2Ffe41eb13a9cec86545c6f901456305f8.jpg%2FPRa3H7aNGM3mYWrS2a6B5gU3PoqeuqSFSPOT_2Lzk_8&h=de3a05f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全場精華<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lwQE4QsV-6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlwQE4QsV-6w&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e1eb2b7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lwQE4QsV-6w</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UyWLSILiMw14GBkx70.kSw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/382317f5897496f9dfb276304a50101c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUyWLSILiMw14GBkx70.kSw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F382317f5897496f9dfb276304a50101c&h=96ef4da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n體藝「美斯」發威！今屆精英賽有絕佳表現的「體藝美斯」陳傲軒，8強領軍對陣哈羅國際學校繼續有好表現，個人貢獻1入球2助攻，協助體藝以4：0大勝。其中他的入球堪稱表演，憑著一己之力連過三關，再射遠柱破網，這一球確實有「真．美斯」的影子。<br />\n<br />\n上半場體藝與哈羅互交白卷，換邊後才正式好戲上演。下半場開賽僅1分鐘，「體藝美斯」陳傲軒左路以一招「恩尼斯達式」過人，殺入底線傳中，伏兵門前的陸俊賢無人看管下勁射破網。落後一球的哈羅傾力反撲，但後防大意再失一球&mdash;哈羅門將與中堅溝通出錯，門將出迎時中堅卻將球頂後，體藝前鋒鄭焯軒成為幸運兒，衝前射入空門。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2494189/org/8208f30011fcf6cc6eddb2a9d39270e2.jpg/OGu0PV_C1HdBS-kMm5efx7NVjSHUeYyPknp25rh6duY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2494189%2Forg%2F8208f30011fcf6cc6eddb2a9d39270e2.jpg%2FOGu0PV_C1HdBS-kMm5efx7NVjSHUeYyPknp25rh6duY&h=c946d887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n餘下賽事就是「體藝美斯」陳傲軒的個人表演時間，先開出角球給遠柱隊友林子山撞入；臨完場前兩分鐘，他於中場線接應傳送後馬上起動，先以速度爆過哈羅一名守衛，再於左路一扭二扣大位，「K角位」燙射遠柱破網，為體藝鎖定4：0的戰果。整個入球動作一氣呵成，絕對是今屆精英賽金球之一。<br />\n<br />\n「美斯」上網睇片學盤扭<br />\n「體藝美斯」陳傲軒今場比賽中的盤扭，並不是純粹天份所致，後天努力同樣重要。他說︰「賽前知道哈羅球員非常高大，我有上網觀看一些短片，研究如何應付高大防守球員。今場我在他們的盲點不停走動，再跑出來接應，這樣我就有空間去作盤扭、傳球。」他認為球隊與進軍旺角大球場踢決賽已經愈來愈近，「起初抽籤時見到我們16強會對拔萃（男書院），有感旺角場與我們很遙遠。直至今場殺入4強，才發覺決賽離我們只是一步之遙。」足球精英賽尚餘兩輪賽事，且看「體藝美斯」今年能夠將體藝帶到多遠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2494188/org/127a4c03f3c3bddd4ad85be665b05b87.jpg/sX4G6AhDvAPi91IT5KNg3FOMg-_cA5i8D99BgyXfQYM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2494188%2Forg%2F127a4c03f3c3bddd4ad85be665b05b87.jpg%2FsX4G6AhDvAPi91IT5KNg3FOMg-_cA5i8D99BgyXfQYM&h=123da06c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n體藝門將何家俊今仗面對哈羅多番勁射仍力保不失，應記一功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uE2d3dSmDg5Ey_nhMWFADw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sportsroad.hk/63703178e2075abe4476c8c0993f7a9b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuE2d3dSmDg5Ey_nhMWFADw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F63703178e2075abe4476c8c0993f7a9b&h=962ea48d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2494186/org/0ad8c684c05820ce1359509d46152536.jpg/1XIB0ZqW5lbGzp2jc46iJNECxOAaiSYvovsAPIj7ADw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2494186%2Forg%2F0ad8c684c05820ce1359509d46152536.jpg%2F1XIB0ZqW5lbGzp2jc46iJNECxOAaiSYvovsAPIj7ADw&h=62640314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連車尾燈都見唔到 點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e0072cb72b2214af6d6c926ca82d220a5d9d76","tid":1042280,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cb514c0b9fb91c6b6a21396959eb1bf400a5e0a","tid":1042280,"uid":99872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"錯呀<br />\n次圈(八強)詳細戰報<br />\n0900 1號場<br />\n伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學 0：1 喇沙書院 1號場<br />\n<br />\n係1:0至真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"自吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205fb153b00fda629c8eacbc99c7c7282e72fd80","tid":1042280,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"四強<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學</span> 元朗區亞軍  <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2493462/org/8b60ac0d208f7a5a8e28885a32e63783.jpg/DnCrdgV0sJIs5_4j5qpmcBsvKgV-Cpug9BQet_QUHrc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2493462%2Forg%2F8b60ac0d208f7a5a8e28885a32e63783.jpg%2FDnCrdgV0sJIs5_4j5qpmcBsvKgV-Cpug9BQet_QUHrc&h=794cd7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">南島中學</span> D1第五名<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2474787/org/f4e4c87e61f28760caf26cee418ecd91.jpg/T8ZbjIoOSlmcfIiMNmAGO7zuqHXDAh9YdPqZTl76mU4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2474787%2Forg%2Ff4e4c87e61f28760caf26cee418ecd91.jpg%2FT8ZbjIoOSlmcfIiMNmAGO7zuqHXDAh9YdPqZTl76mU4&h=7955c51e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港島中學</span> D2冠軍<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/admin.sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/football_interschool_d2_20181118-19.jpg?resize=800%2C533&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?